Class FavoritePlace

java.lang.Object
edu.cnm.deepdive.nnmhlserver.model.entity.FavoritePlace
@Entity public class FavoritePlace extends Object
Encapsulates the key properties of a favorite place including; favorite place id, city name, place id and place name tied to a User.
